data.description: Welcome to this stunning 4-bedroom, 3-bath Craftsman-style home in the highly sought-after Buford neighborhood, just a stone's throw from the serene Lake Lanier. Ideal for blended families, this home offers a versatile bedroom on the main level, perfect for guests or as a convenient home office or a 5th bedroom at the terrace level. The property boasts exceptional curb appeal with its charming covered front entrance leading into a grand two-story foyer. Inside, discover a beautifully spacious kitchen equipped with a functional island, breakfast bar, and sleek granite counters. The kitchen's modern stainless steel appliances, including a brand-new dishwasher and microwave, blend seamlessly with the elegant sunroom/breakfast room. Relax in the cozy family room, highlighted by a stunning stacked stone fireplace, or step into the sunroom that offers an inviting view of the incredible backyard. This outdoor oasis features a large gunite pool and a heated jacuzzi, perfect for entertaining or unwinding in style. Upstairs, the oversized loft provides flexible space for your lifestyle needs, whether it's a play area, a media room, or a home gym. The finished basement adds even more versatility to this already spacious home. Recent updates include a personal gym area with rubber flooring at the terrace level, a 2 year roof, nice paint inside and out, and plush clean carpeting, ensuring the home is move-in ready. The property is also equipped with three recently installed AC units, ensuring comfort throughout the seasons. Nestled in a neighborhood renowned for its top-rated Lanier schools, this home is an exceptional find for families looking for both luxury and convenience. Don't miss your chance to own this Buford gem!
